                    <span>If you don't have the energy to read the full report, this summary is most helpful in giving you most of the key testimony and conclusions. It is essential reading for all concerned citizens today. Christopher Catherwood, author of CHURCHILL'S FOLLY: HOW WINSTON CHURCHILL CREATED MODERN IRAQ (Carroll and Graf, 2004)</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">What Americans need to read for themselves</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
